data.description: Spectacular single-story custom home on 1.2 fenced acres. This spacious floorplan boasts huge bedrooms & open living spaces. Tile & laminate flooring thruout. Foyer entry leads into the livingroom w/ picture windows overlooking the backyard. Beautiful custom kitchen w/ hardwood cabinets & rangehood cover, quartz countertops & tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances incl. 72" frigidaire built-in refrigerator/freezer. Massive walk-in pantry w/barn door entry. Dining area off kitchen w/built-in hutch. Enormous primary suite separated from the other rooms with access to covered patio, lots of windows for natural light, and a luxurious bath w/ a huge walk-in shower complete w/ 3 shower heads. Tons of granite vanity space jetted soaking tub & a walk-in closet. 3 of the 4 secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets & direct-access baths. Separate office tops it all off. Covered patio overlooks spacious lawn area. Attached greenhouse for indoor gardening. Crown Moulding thruout. Tons More!
